snippet.title: Dual Invasion Hard Reset Bullet Assault
snippet.description: A duel based bullet hell shooter programmed in Python and Pygame. Planned are two main gamemodes: basic Duel and Invasion where the idea is to push the enemy back to his core, then destroy it. The game will have 6 different, japanesey characters and combines light strategy elements with a versus-based bullet hell shooter experience. My first real project (and reintroduction to python) that's coming up at a good pace.

snippet.title: QuaaxTM
snippet.description: QuaaxTM is a PHP ISO/IEC 13250 Topic Maps engine which implements PHPTMAPI. This enables developers to work against a standardized API. QuaaxTM uses MySQL with InnoDB or MariaDB with XtraDB as storage engine and benefits from transaction support and referential integrity.
